songs.title: Good Day
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Today is gonna be a good day

[Verse]
Strange sound in my mind
I can not find
I  just want to fight
Dark blood in my arms (Yeah, yeah)
In the riots, bloody rain
I can't kill you or anyone
Running from nothing will serve
You only need two fists and then to fight
I need to protect myself
I think he would kill me

Three hundred thirty-three
Three hundred thirty-three (Aye, aye)
